RDATE000   MOVE     "    4",FLDID
           CALL     GETPOSIT
           MOVE     SP70,CDAY
           MOVE     CMM,CMON
           MOVE     CYY,CYEAR
           MOVE     CCC,CCENT
           CALL     KEYDATE
